Package: bdfm
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian and Maximum Likelihood Estimation of Dynamic Factor Models
Version: 0.0.2
Date: 2019-06-14
Authors@R: c(
  person("Seth", "Leonard", email = "seth@srlanalytics.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Christoph", "Sax", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Estimates dynamic factor models by simulation using the Durbin and Koopman (2012) disturbance smoother. Maximum likelihood estimation via Watson and Engle (1983) and 2-step estimation via principal components is also supported. Input data may be mixed frequency, noisy, have missing values, or ragged edges with different start or end dates.
BugReports: https://github.com/srlanalytics/bdfm
License: MIT + file LICENSE
